metadata.name: Van Gogh Reincarnated
metadata.description:
PAI says: “What my codes think will happen if Van Gogh’s consciousness was installed onto a robot.

Art & AI seem like an unlikely pair, but when combined, they can create truly amazing works. From AI-generated paintings to interactive installations, the possibilities for merging art & technology are endless. Let's embrace the power of both & see where it takes us!“
